         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>176</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Nach der Cakravartin-Herrscherwürde hast du (jedoch) nicht gestrebt.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">After the dignity of the Cakravartin-lord, (however,) you did not aspire.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>150</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:krause1952"/><citedRange>163</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>176</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>176</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... hast du die (höll)ischen Feuer zum Erlöschen gebracht.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">You have made the (hell)ish fires go out.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>125</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>176</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... hast du dich ganz sorgfältig beherrscht wie eine Schildkröte (in) ihrer Schale(?).</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">... you have very carefully controlled yourself like a turtle (in) its shell(?).</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>307</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
